Mingle Card Editor
---------------------------

A Chrome extension, will automatically turn Mingle Card page to editable sections.

Inspired by Smallest-Federated-Wiki project.

Install
==============

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/bbfhdoemhdmeelmfnppcgdojljeamokp

User Reference
==============

* Double click to create/edit a section
* Double return to create a new section following editing section
* Drag&Drop to add&upload images/attachments
* When you're editing a section
  * Cmd/Ctl + s to save
  * Click outside of the editor to save
  * ESC to cancel editing

Limit
==============

Only works with Mingle 12.1 or higher version.
